    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade FD3S RX-7, maintained to an exacting mechanical standard. The 13B-REW power plant exhibits exceptional compression across all rotor faces, fed by a factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger system with zero shaft play and a pristine vacuum line network. This chassis retains its original aluminum double-wishbone suspension geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring the precise turn-in and neutral handling characteristics intended by Mazda's engineers. The cooling system has been meticulously preserved to prevent heat soak, and the drivetrain remains unmodified. With flawless paint depth and a showroom-spec interior, this specimen represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering.",
